features: forewing with three submarginal cells, tentorial pit located at the intersection of outer antennal and epistomal sutures, mandible simple, metapostnotum pubescent (
Figs. 3
, 
7
), mid tibial spur finely toothed, lateral fovea of T2 shallow, metasoma lacking yellow markings; males with S6 presenting a wide U-shaped emargination (
